     FALRWP10 IF  E           K        DISK
     FALRWP11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FALRWP12 O   F     512            DISK
      **************************************************************************
     E                    WNO        10  6
     E                    WDT        10  8 0
     E                    WBX        11  6 0
